name: CupCake Tee
description:
White CUPCAKE tee!

Gorgeous girls white cotton  Tee with flared sleeves, hand embellished with CUPCAKE fabric. A strip of the fabric featuring CUPCAKES adorns the front and a smaller square is hand embellished on the back.

Size 1 currently on offer, message me if you would prefer a different size.

All my tees are one-off creations so yours may vary slightly, but only slightly, from the picture here.
